query:
SELECT 
  brand,
  COUNT(*) as total_products,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND description != '' THEN 1 END) as verified,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN description IS NULL OR description = '' THEN 1 END) as unverified,
  ROUND(COUNT(CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND description != '' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1) as verified_rate
FROM products
GROUP BY brand
HAVING unverified > 0
ORDER BY total_products DESC
LIMIT 15;
